<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l4">von vvertheim vnd eẅr beredt ıſt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd auf nu <expan>mıtwoche<ex>n</ex></expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l5">vns ſolt <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeın . als eẅch eẅr freẅnde wol geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l6">wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Daʒ <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von vvertheım <expan>Cappla<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l7"><expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Nıclas genant . auf dıſʒ ʒeıt / ʒu <expan>Sıgmu<ex>n</ex>d</expan> <expan>Strom<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l9">vnd <expan>ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt vnd Jm geſagt hat 
