<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l10">vvertheim ſölıch nötlıch ſache <expan>angeſtoſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey daʒ er des <expan>obgenan<ex>ten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_176_r1l11">tags niht <expan>geſuche<ex>n</ex></expan> mug / da wıſſe ſıch eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> nach ʒu <expan>rıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
